<h1>Audit (A-09-12-02038)</h1>

<h2>05-29-2013<br />
Palmetto GBA, LLC, Inappropriately Paid Hospitals' Medicare Claims Subject to the Postacute Care Transfer Policy in Jurisdiction 1</h2>

<h2 class="line">Complete Report</h2>

